{"tid":108983,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我應該係唯一一個無食過翠華嘅人","createTime":"2017-02-05T15:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T23:51:38.000Z","uid":39305,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b74b6fabec63e19119cfcf7598f3d4a2a15577f","tid":108983,"uid":39305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"做7-8年前食個餐都已經6-70蚊.<br />\n<br />\n係門口行過見到已經唔會想入去食.<br />\n<br />\n朋友話要食翠華的話我都會反對. <br />\n<br />\n我話唔值.<br />\n<br />\n啱啱見到毒果話翠華又加價啦.<br />\n<br />\n真係忍唔住同食翠華嘅人講一句 &quot;我真係恭喜你&quot;"},{"pid":"88ac01fb0f7551f739b53b436b9b47f2b9efc28e","tid":108983,"uid":45506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"大把人都冇食過 好出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba801816ec82f125fe6a55788b9aa4d612a9f9c","tid":108983,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"我都未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f83eda98e4ca19035977969e024a1e5ae74e60","tid":108983,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"看得自己那麼高"},{"pid":"8e70b69ecfe79e87cb3b34ce3f2cf9413049693b","tid":108983,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"第一次入嗰陣望一望個價錢就好瀟灑咁行返出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6324acd8bb07826d707f046b856012670a2a44ed","tid":108983,"uid":43350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我廿頭，都未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aaced108d7bdb411baebf5442d8c9e57b2795d0","tid":108983,"uid":60256,"like":0